If it is open you can add it, and given that it is only a one unit class you probably didn't miss relatively all that much. 

———

As someone who is currently in the class, you’ve not missed anything but one survey, and the points for that (which are very little) can be made up later in the semester. If you are going to add the class, I’d recommend doing so today and joining the class piazza so you don’t miss the next survey. We have not had any graded work beyond that, and class is all discussion based.
